        "accordion_xfbPBi": {
          "type": "accordion",
          "settings": {
            "show_below_gallery": true,
            "icon": "none",
            "title": "Materials",
            "content": "<p><strong>Gold Vermeil </strong>- A thick layer of real 18ct gold bonded to solid sterling silver - up to 25x thicker than standard plating. Designed to last, crafted to shine, made to hold meaning.</p><p><strong>Solid 925 sterling silver</strong> - finished with rhodium - a rare metal from the platinum family. This bright, durable layer protects against tarnish and keeps every piece shining beautifully.</p><p><strong>Protective anti-tarnish coating</strong> that helps preserve shine and colour over time. It adds an invisible shield against daily wear, so your jewelry stays as beautiful as the day you received it. </p><p><strong>Conflict-free simulated diamonds,</strong> hand-set for a flawless finish.</p><p><strong>Sparkle Index (Refractive Index)</strong></p><p>Our stones: <strong>2.18 </strong>| Natural diamonds: <strong>2.41</strong></p><p><strong>Durability (MOHS Hardness) </strong></p><p>Our stones: <strong>8.5 </strong>| Natural diamonds: <strong>10</strong></p>",
            "liquid": "",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "accordion_yUkiTP": {
          "type": "accordion",
          "settings": {
            "show_below_gallery": true,
            "icon": "none",
            "title": "Promise 2 Year Warranty",
            "content": "<p>Your jewelry is more than an accessory - it’s a symbol of love, commitment, and life’s cherished moments. That’s why every piece comes with a <strong>2-year warranty</strong> for complete peace of mind.</p><p>We’ll <strong>repair</strong> any manufacturing faults free of charge or <strong>replace</strong> your piece if a repair isn’t possible.</p><p>If your warranty has expired, or any accidental damage has occurred please reach out. We’ll still do our best to help with <strong>repairs or replacements at a reduced fee</strong>.</p><p><a href=\"https://thepromiseco.com/pages/2-year-warranty\" title=\"https://thepromiseco.com/pages/2-year-warranty\">View full warranty details here.</a></p>",
            "liquid": "",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "accordion_jB4gQj": {
          "type": "accordion",
          "disabled": true,
          "settings": {
            "show_below_gallery": true,
            "icon": "none",
            "title": "Shipping",
            "content": "<p><strong>UK Shipping</strong></p><p>We ship directly from our UK warehouse with care and speed. <strong>Free 24-hour delivery</strong> on all orders over <strong>£130. </strong>Any orders before 1pm UK time are dispatched on the same day </p><p><strong>24 hour & 48 hour delivery Mon-Saturday </strong>available at checkout. Every parcel is fully tracked and beautifully packaged - ready to gift the moment it arrives.</p><p><em>Please note we do not ship on weekends or bank holidays.</em></p><p><strong>US Shipping </strong>All US orders are shipped from our US warehouse for faster, tariff-free delivery. <strong>We are proud to be in the top 1% of USA businesses for speed and reliability. </strong></p><p><strong>Free express shipping</strong> on orders over <strong>$220</strong></p><p>Any orders before 1pm UK time are dispatched on the same day. </p><p>For zones 1-8 our deliver time is 1-3 days No hidden customs fees, no delays.</p><p>Every parcel is fully tracked and beautifully packaged - ready to gift the moment it arrives.</p>",
            "liquid": "",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
